  <h4>Expandable tray</h4>

  <p>If content in Zone 2 includes a menu and when that menu text is selected, an <strong>expandable tray</strong> will appear. It is divided into three parts and is styled the same across all themes.</p>

  <ol>
    <li><strong>Tab</strong> - Visually indicates what menu is expanded</li>
    <li><strong>Tray</strong> - The area where content or other components can be placed</li>
    <li><strong>Overlay</strong> - A transparent background that helps elevate the component above the page underneath</li>
  </ol>

